{"tid":1885012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧炳強話跟成龍學做做警察  一齊嚟睇吓佢學咗啲乜","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T07:45:37.000Z","uid":249653,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"196d965d121ea9adf089294f08548344e00cc7f6","tid":1885012,"uid":249653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>警察故事(1985)</strong><br />\n- 唔服從警方通輯令<br />\n- 脅持上司離開警局<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警察故事續集 (1988)</strong><br />\n- 比人嘲笑而大打出手 (私了)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 要求警方提供贖款，贖返女友<br />\n- 聽從匪徒要求，攜帶炸彈進入警處<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警察故事3 : 超級警察(1992)</strong><br />\n- (做臥底，比人被揭穿前做乜都合理)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警察故事4：簡單任務(1996)</strong><br />\n- 以為美國CIA吹水，去到烏克蘭先知事態嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新警察故事(2004)</strong><br />\n- 指揮大意﹐導致小隊全軍覆沒<br />\n- 遭羈押時有同僚包庇，私下從羈留室逃出<br />\n- 私自與匪徒在會展天台對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>警察故事2013(2013)</strong><br />\n- (名係警察，實際上係公安)<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/entertainment/5akmvv2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2F5akmvv2.html&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=fea3300c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/entertainment/5akmvv2.html</a>  / Wiki"},{"pid":"3ae49e54496b3dca310f4a4317180f803bb6ed80","tid":1885012,"uid":253826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa07ff1a3d1d054c92a8e7e0c83b65c8af86aacd","tid":1885012,"uid":35456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"898b907e5680a8f60df008a84cabcd91463943